     C                     ADD  W1USD2    W@USD2
     C                     ADD  W1USD3    W@USD3
     C                     MOVELW1OMIT    W@OMIT  1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ ABMWP111                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     EXSR #SB500
      *
     CSR         ESB400    ENDSR
